{"tid":2353513,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎影響戲院3度停業全年票房大跌72% 黃子華《乜代宗師》成港片冠軍","createTime":"2021-01-04T20:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T16:05:54.000Z","uid":130626,"like":11,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"1044cd014cd090e06ac52480b88b2a2a7058349c","tid":2353513,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T20:31:12.000Z","msg":"黃子華《乜代宗師》成華語冠軍<br />\n去黃子華自導自演的《乜代宗師》以2,945萬元（詳見附表）成港片冠軍，蔡思韵、劉俊謙主演，周冠威導演的《幻愛》以1,525萬元位列亞軍，季軍是黃百鳴的《家有囍事2020》，累計票房1,191萬元。至於全年總冠軍在毫無懸念下，由《Tenet天能》（Tenet）以5,491萬元奪得，全年亞軍是停院前仍在上映的《鬼滅之刃劇場版 無限列車篇》，累計票房2,858萬元。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210104/KEJWZXR53VCIPN3IFJP3BBA2HA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210104%2FKEJWZXR53VCIPN3IFJP3BBA2HA%2F&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=d9ff2643\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210104%2FKEJWZXR53VCIPN3IFJP3BBA2HA%2F&h=99f4601c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210104/KEJWZXR53VCIPN3IFJP3BBA2HA/</a>"},{"pid":"0c74bf81e3e3873dd5bc9c54b00821496c083faf","tid":2353513,"uid":236891,"like":28,"dislike":48,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T21:22:25.000Z","msg":"套扮黃既垃圾片咁都做到冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完全反映呢一年啲黃店煮屎垃圾當道啲連衛兵重要嗌好好味呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4acfc01d315cfd541979cb6a7728b286d6d45993","tid":2353513,"uid":256837,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T21:31:30.000Z","msg":"幻愛正好多"},{"pid":"ed4d81ded1599535d8e91ed110cdcb00634d666e","tid":2353513,"uid":59920,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T21:36:11.000Z","msg":"兒登男神唔屌得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig